// Your Concept (include exact sign text in quotes)
{cursor}

// Text & Signage - Shop Sign
Close-up photograph of a storefront sign mounted above the shop entrance. The sign is legible and sharply rendered, with the exact wording the user specified reproduced cleanly in its described font and color. Surrounding storefront details support the scene: brickwork or painted wood facade, a recessed doorway, small window reflections. Warm tungsten light from inside the shop spills onto the sign, natural late-afternoon ambient light outside. Film-like color, subtle grain, realistic materials and weathering.

Negative Prompt:
gibberish text, misspelled, distorted letters, blurry, low quality, watermark, logo

// Your Concept (include exact sign text in quotes)
{cursor}

// Text & Signage - Neon Sign
A vibrant neon sign glowing against a dark nighttime wall. The exact text specified by the user is formed from bent glass tubes with visible gas-filled glow and faint halation around each stroke. Pink-magenta, electric blue, or acid green neon hues, with subtle reflections on a damp pavement or glass window below. Atmospheric haze, slight lens bloom, shallow depth of field. Cinematic urban night photography, film grain, strong color contrast against deep blacks.

Negative Prompt:
gibberish text, misspelled, distorted letters, daylight, flat lighting, blurry, low quality, watermark, logo

// Your Concept (supply exact menu items + prices)
{cursor}

// Text & Signage - Menu Board
A hand-lettered chalkboard menu board mounted inside a small cafe or restaurant. The menu items and prices specified by the user are rendered legibly in chalk or paint-marker typography, arranged as a readable list with clear section headers. Wooden frame around the board, warm ambient light from hanging pendant lamps, subtle background blur of the interior. Natural chalk texture, minor smudges, realistic handwritten feel. Color palette of cream, dark forest green, warm brown, pastel accents.

Negative Prompt:
gibberish text, jumbled letters, unreadable, blurry, low quality, watermark, logo

// Your Concept (include exact graffiti text)
{cursor}

// Text & Signage - Graffiti Wall
A weathered urban wall photographed straight-on, dominated by a large spray-paint graffiti piece containing the exact text specified by the user. Bold drippy letterforms with layered outlines, fill colors, and halo highlights. Tagged walls usually show surrounding stickers, paste-ups, concrete cracks, rusted downpipes. Overcast diffused daylight so colors read true. Documentary street-photo aesthetic with honest urban grit, realistic textures, no stylization.

Negative Prompt:
gibberish text, clean studio background, blurry, low quality, watermark, logo

// Your Concept (include exact destination names)
{cursor}

// Text & Signage - Vintage Signpost
A weathered wooden signpost at a rural crossroads with multiple arrow-shaped planks pointing in different directions. Each plank is clearly legible with the destination names specified by the user, painted in cream or yellow on dark green or faded red, with distances in miles or kilometers below each place name. Aged wood texture with visible grain and nail heads, slight moss on the post, surrounding grass and trees softly out of focus. Overcast or golden-hour lighting, muted color palette, pastoral travel-photography feel.

Negative Prompt:
gibberish text, unreadable, modern signage, blurry, low quality, watermark, logo

// Your Concept (supply title + numbered step labels)
{cursor}

// Infographic - Process Diagram
Educational infographic on a light beige vintage paper background. The title supplied by the user is rendered prominently at the top center in a bold serif or slab font. Below it, numbered step blocks are arranged in a Z-flow or grid layout, connected by dotted or arrow lines. Each step has a small hand-drawn icon, a short header label, and one or two lines of body text. Warm earthy palette of browns, creams, deep reds, olive greens. Corners decorated with small hand-drawn flourishes relevant to the topic. Clean typography, clear hierarchy, textbook-illustration aesthetic.

Negative Prompt:
gibberish text, jumbled labels, modern minimalist, blurry, low quality, watermark, logo

// Your Concept (specify species + panel count)
{cursor}

// Infographic - Species Chart
Educational comic-book-style infographic showing a row of vertical panels side by side, each panel depicting one species in hand-drawn illustration style. The top title specified by the user spans the width of the composition in bold caps. Each panel has a species name header, a detailed drawing of the animal/plant, and two or three short annotated facts with tiny arrows pointing to anatomical features. Earthy watercolor palette, cream backgrounds, bold outlines. Nature-encyclopedia aesthetic, scientific yet approachable.

Negative Prompt:
gibberish text, modern infographic, photograph, blurry, low quality, watermark, logo

// Your Concept (supply title + chronological entries)
{cursor}

// Infographic - Timeline
A horizontal historical timeline infographic. A thick central timeline bar runs left to right across the composition, with date markers and labeled event nodes alternating above and below. The title supplied by the user sits at the top. Each event node has a small illustrated icon, a bold year, a short event name, and a one-sentence description. Muted editorial palette of ink blue, burgundy, antique gold, cream paper. Clean modern editorial layout with restrained typography.

Negative Prompt:
gibberish text, vertical layout, blurry, low quality, watermark, logo

// Your Concept (supply dish name + ingredients + steps)
{cursor}

// Infographic - Recipe Infographic
A single-page recipe infographic with the dish name supplied by the user as the top title in a warm hand-lettered display font. Below, an ingredients column on the left lists each item with a small hand-drawn illustration, and a numbered steps column on the right shows each cooking step with an icon and short instruction. Decorative sprigs, spoons, and ingredient sketches fill corners. Warm kitchen palette of cream, terracotta, olive, deep red. Cookbook-illustration aesthetic, clean readable layout, print-quality typography.

Negative Prompt:
gibberish text, modern minimal, photograph, blurry, low quality, watermark, logo

// Your Concept (supply topic + key terms to label)
{cursor}

// Infographic - Science Infographic
A wide-format science-education infographic on a deep navy or dark teal background. The topic title supplied by the user appears at the top in a clean sans-serif. The composition is divided into two or three zones, each explaining one concept with a labeled 3D-rendered model or diagram, short caption, and thin connecting leader lines. Accurate anatomical or structural details, chalk-white or pale-gold typography, subtle grid or blueprint lines in the background. Scientific publication aesthetic, calm authoritative feel.

Negative Prompt:
gibberish text, cute illustration, children's book, blurry, low quality, watermark, logo

