A screen-printed concert poster for the act, date, and venue supplied by the user. The band name dominates in distorted custom typography reflecting the genre — psychedelic swirls, punk cut-paper, metal blackletter, indie hand-drawn. Date and venue information appear in supporting type below. The central image is a bold graphic illustration with limited-palette screen-print aesthetic, heavy ink textures, halftone dot patterns. Gig-poster tradition feel, 2-4 color riso or screen-print look.

