// Your Concept (supply title + optional subtitle)
{cursor}

// Poster - Minimalist Poster
A minimalist graphic poster using the title supplied by the user as the sole dominant type element. A single bold geometric or symbolic graphic element anchors the composition — a stark silhouette, a single shape, or a clever negative-space gestalt. Generous whitespace, two to three colors maximum, strong grid-based layout. Swiss design / Helvetica tradition, museum print-quality feel. Restrained, confident, high-concept.

Negative Prompt:
gibberish text, busy composition, many elements, blurry, low quality, watermark, logo

// Your Concept (supply opposing concepts + overlay text)
{cursor}

// Poster - Split-Screen Conceptual
A conceptual poster with vertical split-screen composition. The left half depicts one side of the contrast supplied by the user, the right half depicts its opposite — lit and colored to emphasize the dichotomy. The overlay text supplied by the user is placed prominently in a bold sans-serif, breaking across the seam or floating on one half. Smaller supporting text blocks in the corners contain technical-looking metadata. Cinematic sci-fi editorial aesthetic, high-contrast lighting, deliberate color temperature divide.

Negative Prompt:
gibberish text, single subject, flat lighting, blurry, low quality, watermark, logo

// Your Concept (supply panel count + dialogue per panel)
{cursor}

// Comic Panels - Multi-Panel Comic
A comic page divided into the panel grid specified by the user, with thin black borders between panels and small white gutters. Each panel depicts one beat of the user's story in ink-and-watercolor illustration style. Expressive line art, cool blue-gray limited palette, selective color accents for emphasis. Speech balloons and captions contain exactly the dialogue supplied by the user in clean comic-lettering typography. Western indie-graphic-novel or modern webcomic feel, narrative pacing, consistent character design across panels.

Negative Prompt:
gibberish dialogue, inconsistent character, photograph, blurry, low quality, watermark, logo

// Your Concept (supply scene + dialogue)
{cursor}

// Comic Panels - Manga Page
A black-and-white manga page with a dynamic irregular panel layout — large establishing panel, smaller action beats, close-up reaction shot. Screen-tone patterns for shading, crisp pen-and-ink linework, expressive speed lines where action demands. Japanese comic lettering in speech bubbles and sound-effect katakana containing exactly the text supplied by the user. Shōnen or seinen manga aesthetic, confident brushwork, sharp contrast, no color except pure black ink on off-white paper.

Negative Prompt:
gibberish text, full color, western comic style, blurry, low quality, watermark, logo

// Your Concept (supply scene + shot descriptions)
{cursor}

// Comic Panels - Film Storyboard
A film storyboard sheet with a 2×3 or 3×2 grid of panels, each showing one shot of the sequence supplied by the user. Rough gestural pencil-and-marker drawings inside each frame, camera and action notation handwritten below each panel. Arrows indicate camera movement or subject motion. Panel numbers in corners. Professional pre-production storyboard aesthetic, working-drawing energy, not final illustration.

Negative Prompt:
gibberish annotations, finished illustration, color, blurry, low quality, watermark, logo

// Your Concept (supply 3-4 panel gag + dialogue)
{cursor}

// Comic Panels - Newspaper Comic Strip
A three or four panel horizontal newspaper comic strip. Each panel has clean thin black borders and flat simple color palette. Characters drawn in a consistent friendly cartoon style with exaggerated expressions driving a short gag. Dialogue in speech balloons uses exactly the text supplied by the user. Title of the strip may appear in the first panel. Classic Sunday-funnies aesthetic — Peanuts, Calvin & Hobbes, Garfield tradition — approachable, readable, humor-driven.

Negative Prompt:
gibberish text, complex rendering, dark tones, blurry, low quality, watermark, logo

// Your Concept (supply topic + learning beats)
{cursor}

// Comic Panels - Educational Comic
An educational comic page that teaches the topic supplied by the user across a sequence of five or six panels. A friendly narrator character guides the reader, explaining concepts in clear speech balloons with the exact dialogue supplied. Each panel has a short caption box reinforcing the lesson. Bright flat-color illustration, children's-book friendly, clean line art, rounded shapes. Warm welcoming palette, schoolbook or science-comic aesthetic.

Negative Prompt:
gibberish text, dark moody, horror, blurry, low quality, watermark, logo

// Your Concept (describe app + what screen shows)
{cursor}

// UI Mockup - Phone App Screen
A photorealistic render of a modern smartphone held in-hand, angled slightly, with the screen showing the app UI supplied by the user. The UI contains realistic and legible interface elements — status bar with time and battery, navigation headers, buttons with readable labels, content cards with sample text, tab bar at the bottom. Modern iOS or Android design language, crisp pixel-grid alignment. Soft studio lighting, subtle reflections on the glass, shallow depth of field on the hand and background.

Negative Prompt:
gibberish UI text, blurry screen, low-res UI, blurry, low quality, watermark, logo

// Your Concept (describe website + sections visible)
{cursor}

// UI Mockup - Desktop Browser
A wide-aspect screenshot of a desktop browser showing the website described by the user. The browser chrome is realistic with visible tab title, address bar, bookmarks row. The webpage below has a top navigation bar, a hero banner with headline and subtext, sectioned content cards or grids, and a footer. All visible text is legible and reads as real copy on the subject. Clean modern web design, generous whitespace, consistent typography hierarchy, subtle shadows and rounded corners. Retina-sharp pixel render.

Negative Prompt:
gibberish text, blurry UI, inconsistent typography, blurry, low quality, watermark, logo

// Your Concept (describe watch face + data shown)
{cursor}

// UI Mockup - Smartwatch UI
A photorealistic close-up of a modern smartwatch worn on a wrist, showing the watch face described by the user. The display contains legible time, date, and complications with short readable labels for heart rate, steps, weather, or notifications. Vibrant OLED colors on deep-black background, crisp anti-aliased text, polished metal or silicone strap details. Soft diffused ambient light, subtle reflection on the display glass, shallow depth of field.

