{cursor}

// Sticker Pack - Line Sticker Pack
A grid layout sticker pack sheet — typically 4 rows by 6 columns — featuring the character supplied by the user in a range of expressions and poses, each in its own cell. Each sticker has a short caption in a cute hand-lettered font describing the emotion or phrase. Vibrant hand-drawn chibi illustration style with clean outlines, soft cel-shading, small simple backgrounds or pure white cells. Consistent character design across all cells. Line or Discord sticker aesthetic.

