{cursor}

// Sticker Pack - Emoji Grid
A clean grid of custom emoji icons on a plain white background. Each cell contains one circular or rounded emoji-style face depicting a different expression of the subject supplied by the user — laughing, crying, heart-eyes, angry, sleeping, thinking, etc. Simple bold shapes, glossy highlights on top, soft shadow beneath. Vibrant saturated colors, strong silhouettes, readable at tiny sizes. Apple/Twemoji/Discord emoji aesthetic.

