A reference sheet of reaction faces arranged in a grid, each cell labeled with a short mood word in a clean sans-serif. The subject supplied by the user appears in every cell with a distinctly different facial expression and posture, consistent character design throughout. Manga-inspired expression chart aesthetic — eyebrows, mouth, eye shape exaggerated per emotion. Clean flat-color illustration, light gridlines, cream or pure-white background.

