// Flashcard - Language Flashcard
A vertical rectangular language-learning flashcard with decorative border framing the whole card. The upper two-thirds shows a detailed illustration of the concept supplied by the user in a style fitting the target language's culture. The lower third is a centered text block containing the word in the target script, its romanization if applicable, and the English translation, each on its own line in clear hierarchy. Aged-paper or themed background texture, consistent color palette tied to the cultural setting. Educational flashcard aesthetic.

