// Flashcard - Character Profile Card
A trading-card style character profile with the character name supplied by the user as the top header in bold stylized typography. A large character illustration fills the upper portion inside a decorative frame. Below, a stat block with labeled rows — class, level, abilities, short bio — rendered in small clean readable type. Themed border styled to the character's genre (fantasy scroll, sci-fi hud panel, trading-card foil). Print-ready card aesthetic, consistent internal design language.

