{cursor}

// Flashcard - Study Card
A single educational study card on a clean cream or pastel background. The topic title supplied by the user sits at the top in bold sans-serif. Below, a small central illustration or diagram of the concept, followed by three to five bullet facts in crisp legible body type. Small icons next to each bullet for visual interest. Soft rounded corners on the card, gentle drop shadow. Modern educational app aesthetic, Quizlet / Anki / Duolingo feel.

