// Photorealistic - Cinematic Still
Cinematic still from a prestige feature film, shot on anamorphic lenses at 2.39:1 aspect. Strong directional lighting with deep shadow falloff, subtle volumetric atmosphere, film-grain texture across the entire frame. Color grade balanced toward cool shadows and warm highlights, or a distinctive single-color wash. Natural skin with real pores and micro-texture, no plastic smoothness. Sharp focus on subject, smooth bokeh in background, honest film aesthetic.

