// Photorealistic - Documentary
Documentary photography in the tradition of National Geographic and long-form photojournalism. Natural available light only, unposed candid moment, environmental storytelling with rich contextual detail. Mid-range focal length that preserves spatial relationships. Honest imperfect skin, real clothing wear, authentic expressions. Earthy true-to-life color, no heavy grade. Sharp focus on the subject's eyes, slight ambient bokeh.

Negative Prompt:
studio lighting, posed, plastic skin, airbrushed, cartoon, blurry, low quality, watermark, logo

