// Photorealistic - Golden Hour Portrait
Portrait photograph captured in the last hour before sunset. Low warm sun rakes across the subject from behind, creating a rim light on hair and shoulders and a soft key light wrapping the face. Atmospheric haze carries golden particles through the air. Natural skin texture with visible warmth and subtle sheen, honest micro-detail. Shallow depth of field with creamy bokeh, 85mm equivalent framing, gentle film-like color grade.

