High-end fashion editorial in the style of a Vogue or Harper's Bazaar spread. Strong directional studio or natural light sculpting the subject with bold shadow shapes. Confident editorial pose, impeccable styling, considered color palette matching wardrobe to setting. Shot on medium format equivalent with 85mm to 110mm lens, shallow depth of field. Natural skin texture with subtle pore detail, no airbrushed smoothness. Print-quality tonal range.

