Candid street photography shot on 35mm equivalent, Henri Cartier-Bresson decisive-moment tradition. Natural available light, honest composition with strong geometry, environmental context telling a story beyond the subject. Monochromatic or muted color, authentic grit and detail. Slight motion-implied energy, sharp focus on the key subject, shallow to mid depth of field.

