// Photorealistic - Neon Night
First-person urban night photograph. Narrow wet streets with strong perspective depth, towering architecture with fire escapes and signage on both sides. Saturated neon signage — red, blue, magenta, acid yellow — reflecting in puddles and wet pavement. Strong cyan-blue ambient with warm orange-red accents, volumetric mist in the air, cinematic color separation. Film-like grain, honest low-light color behavior.

