Extreme macro photograph at life-size or greater magnification. Tack-sharp focus on the tiny subject, exaggerated surface texture and micro-detail visible at inspection distance. Extremely shallow depth of field with creamy defocused foreground and background, soft backlight picking out translucent edges. Natural color reproduction, gentle ambient fill, laboratory or studio macro aesthetic.

